title: Man Feeding Baby Dark Skin Tone
description: A man with dark skin tone feeding a baby, symbolizing care, nurturing, and parental love. This represents a father figure actively involved in childcare.

Apple's characteristic glossy shading and soft, rounded forms highlight the loving interaction between the father and child. This emoji powerfully symbolizes parenthood, nurturing, and familial bonds, offering a touching visual representation of love and support in digital communication.
